The Julekalender (norwegian)

      "The Julekalender" is a Christmas story about three "nisser"          
      who have to go from the North Pole and back to the "hule"             
      (cave) in the Norwegian province of Trondelag to find the life        
      melody of the head nisse "Good old gammel nok" who is about to        
      die. However they have to watch out for the evil "NÃƒÂ¥sÃƒÂ¥", who          
      during the series comes to live with a potato farmer nearby. The      
      series is based on funny lines containing dialect                     
      (the potato farmer) or a mix between Norwegian and English            
      (the nisses). The lines are repeated in episode after episode,        
      and if a good line occurs, one of the nisses will say
